WEBVTT

00:01:29.530 --> 00:01:34.940
[Our Dazzling Days]

00:01:35.390 --> 00:01:37.710
[Episode 21]

00:01:46.430 --> 00:01:50.160
You still look like a bookworm
when pushing your glasses like that.

00:02:20.650 --> 00:02:23.050
You just took your glasses off,
didn't you?

00:02:24.150 --> 00:02:26.520
The admin staff just asked
the other colleagues

00:02:26.520 --> 00:02:28.720
who left their glasses in the restroom.

00:02:29.800 --> 00:02:31.079
You look better without them.

00:02:31.079 --> 00:02:33.079
You're meeting my direct boss soon,

00:02:33.120 --> 00:02:34.840
Kong Peng, Director
of the Strategic Investment Department.

00:02:34.840 --> 00:02:36.150
He has a Harvard MBA,

00:02:36.310 --> 00:02:38.510
likes to talk about corporate culture,

00:02:38.590 --> 00:02:39.650
and is very shrewd.

00:02:40.110 --> 00:02:43.110
Looking shrewd
doesn't necessarily mean being shrewd.

00:02:43.110 --> 00:02:45.400
People who become directors aren't fools.

00:02:45.400 --> 00:02:47.390
I didn't mention our experience
at the East Chemical Plant.

00:02:47.390 --> 00:02:49.280
This is just a recommendation
between friends.

00:02:49.280 --> 00:02:50.340
Do you understand?

00:02:50.800 --> 00:02:51.530
Understood.

00:02:51.540 --> 00:02:53.280
[Director's Office]

00:02:53.280 --> 00:02:53.870
Come in.

00:02:56.560 --> 00:02:57.490
This is Mr. Kong.

00:02:58.310 --> 00:03:00.230
Mr. Kong, this is Xia Lei.

00:03:03.270 --> 00:03:03.960
Hello.

00:03:06.640 --> 00:03:07.300
Have a seat.

00:03:10.150 --> 00:03:11.560
I'll leave you to it.

00:03:11.970 --> 00:03:12.530
Okay.

00:03:15.800 --> 00:03:18.030
Why do you suddenly
want to work for our company?

00:03:18.030 --> 00:03:20.800
Because your company
is a Fortune 500 enterprise.

00:03:20.800 --> 00:03:22.750
I'm very interested in

00:03:23.150 --> 00:03:24.680
both the company's scale
and corporate culture.

00:03:24.680 --> 00:03:26.800
I believe that working here

00:03:26.800 --> 00:03:29.000
would be a great learning opportunity.

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:31.000
It can improve my learning ability

00:03:31.110 --> 00:03:32.520
and professional skills,

00:03:32.520 --> 00:03:35.850
and allow me to contribute more
to the company in the future.

00:03:36.040 --> 00:03:39.329
Standard answers
seem to be popular lately.

00:03:39.560 --> 00:03:42.000
I've seen a few candidates
these past few days,

00:03:42.000 --> 00:03:44.190
and they answered just like you.

00:03:44.770 --> 00:03:46.930
But you seem to have left out one thing,

00:03:47.190 --> 00:03:49.750
the issue of salary and benefits.

00:03:50.240 --> 00:03:52.300
After all, it's a market economy now.

00:03:52.470 --> 00:03:55.360
Being shy about money
isn't actually a good habit.

00:03:55.680 --> 00:03:58.710
So I assume coming to our company

00:03:59.310 --> 00:04:02.470
has something to do with the salary,
right?

00:04:03.400 --> 00:04:05.590
It does, but...

00:04:06.080 --> 00:04:06.960
not entirely.

00:04:07.430 --> 00:04:09.470
Can you be more specific?

00:04:10.870 --> 00:04:11.560
Your department

00:04:11.560 --> 00:04:14.360
is the newly established
Strategic Investment Department.

00:04:14.360 --> 00:04:15.150
Its main purpose

00:04:15.150 --> 00:04:18.190
is to find the latest investment trends
in China.

00:04:18.720 --> 00:04:22.040
Starting from the third quarter of 2002,

00:04:22.040 --> 00:04:23.870
in the field of innovation investment,

00:04:23.870 --> 00:04:25.000
a lot of capital

00:04:25.000 --> 00:04:26.240
has already flowed into communications

00:04:26.240 --> 00:04:27.510
and IT industries.

00:04:27.510 --> 00:04:29.040
Finding and acquiring

00:04:29.040 --> 00:04:31.040
valuable local Chinese companies

00:04:31.430 --> 00:04:32.750
is definitely the trend.

00:04:32.750 --> 00:04:35.920
I believe this is also
one of your future directions.

00:04:36.190 --> 00:04:37.390
Very comprehensive.

00:04:37.590 --> 00:04:40.000
But the direction is slightly off.

00:04:40.560 --> 00:04:41.960
Let me ask you a question.

00:04:42.360 --> 00:04:45.000
There's a popular saying lately

00:04:45.240 --> 00:04:47.570
that investment bankers are like wolves.

00:04:47.630 --> 00:04:50.720
What is your understanding of this?

00:04:51.720 --> 00:04:53.070
My understanding is that

00:04:53.070 --> 00:04:55.800
investment bankers
need a wolf's sense of smell,

00:04:56.370 --> 00:04:57.770
a wolf's keenness,

00:04:58.720 --> 00:05:00.560
and a wolf's obedience and execution.

00:05:00.560 --> 00:05:02.470
Then do you think

00:05:02.720 --> 00:05:04.360
you have any of that wolf in you?

00:05:04.360 --> 00:05:07.070
I think I have the potential
to become a wolf.

00:05:09.160 --> 00:05:11.190
What's on my resume is my past.

00:05:12.100 --> 00:05:13.900
Those experiences made me grow.

00:05:14.130 --> 00:05:15.570
They made me tougher.

00:05:15.670 --> 00:05:17.600
If you give me this opportunity,

00:05:17.800 --> 00:05:19.910
I will definitely show you
my transformation.

00:05:19.910 --> 00:05:22.640
And what if I don't give you this chance?

00:05:25.590 --> 00:05:27.000
If you reject me,

00:05:28.160 --> 00:05:29.680
I won't change my path.

00:05:29.750 --> 00:05:31.510
I will go to your competitor

00:05:31.510 --> 00:05:32.470
to seek an opportunity.

00:05:32.470 --> 00:05:33.890
When we meet again

00:05:33.920 --> 00:05:35.380
at the negotiation table,

00:05:35.950 --> 00:05:37.950
you will remember what I said today.

00:05:38.530 --> 00:05:40.170
Then we'll wait and see.

00:05:46.580 --> 00:05:47.950
Welcome to Fenlier.

00:05:51.090 --> 00:05:52.220
Thank you, Mr. Kong.

00:06:01.560 --> 00:06:02.420
Zhang Xiaoman!

00:06:03.480 --> 00:06:04.040
Yu.

00:06:04.680 --> 00:06:05.480
Wait a moment.

00:06:07.040 --> 00:06:09.630
Mr. Watanabe, I'm going out for a bit.

00:06:10.500 --> 00:06:11.060
Yes.

00:06:14.430 --> 00:06:15.480
This place is huge.

00:06:15.480 --> 00:06:16.160
Of course.

00:06:17.240 --> 00:06:18.510
Doesn't coming here

00:06:18.800 --> 00:06:20.560
make your blood race?

00:06:21.070 --> 00:06:21.510
It's nice.

00:06:21.510 --> 00:06:23.750
Do you want to go up
and throw a few punches?

00:06:23.750 --> 00:06:24.750
I can't do that.

00:06:26.070 --> 00:06:27.800
You've finally figured it out?

00:06:28.000 --> 00:06:29.270
Well, after I went back
and thought about it,

00:06:29.270 --> 00:06:30.950
I think I can do this job.

00:06:31.870 --> 00:06:32.870
You can do it, huh?

00:06:33.360 --> 00:06:34.159
That's right.

00:06:34.240 --> 00:06:36.310
Why did you come to a foreign country?

00:06:36.310 --> 00:06:38.390
Isn't it to make money?

00:06:38.390 --> 00:06:39.820
Who would complain about
having too much money?

00:06:39.820 --> 00:06:40.750
-Yes.
-Right?

00:06:40.800 --> 00:06:41.630
Yu.

00:06:41.870 --> 00:06:44.430
I can't quit my other job.

00:06:44.920 --> 00:06:46.750
I can come over on holidays

00:06:46.750 --> 00:06:49.040
or when I get off work early.

00:06:49.270 --> 00:06:50.070
No problem.

00:06:50.070 --> 00:06:51.870
We pay by the hour here.

00:06:52.360 --> 00:06:54.220
Just come whenever you have time.

00:06:54.290 --> 00:06:54.800
Okay.

00:06:55.460 --> 00:06:56.750
By the way, well...

00:06:57.800 --> 00:06:59.730
does Madam Zhuang agree with this?

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:03.060
I haven't told her.

00:07:03.800 --> 00:07:04.400
It's fine.

00:07:04.680 --> 00:07:05.360
Alright.

00:07:05.720 --> 00:07:06.870
Since you're here today,

00:07:06.870 --> 00:07:08.830
let's start now,

00:07:08.830 --> 00:07:09.630
-okay?
-Okay.

00:07:10.560 --> 00:07:11.360
Wait a moment.

00:07:11.870 --> 00:07:12.430
Chen.

00:07:12.750 --> 00:07:13.430
Mr. Yu.

00:07:14.160 --> 00:07:15.420
This is Zhang Xiaoman.

00:07:15.630 --> 00:07:16.720
He's our new employee.

00:07:16.720 --> 00:07:18.240
Show him the ropes from now on.

00:07:18.240 --> 00:07:19.000
You got it, Mr. Yu.

00:07:19.000 --> 00:07:20.480
Fill him in on the situation here.

00:07:20.480 --> 00:07:21.410
Show him around.

00:07:21.750 --> 00:07:22.310
Got it.

00:07:22.510 --> 00:07:23.240
Chat away.

00:07:23.240 --> 00:07:24.800
There are fellow countrymen here?

00:07:24.800 --> 00:07:26.390
There are a few Chinese people here.

00:07:26.390 --> 00:07:28.360
What? Do you think
your Japanese is good enough

00:07:28.360 --> 00:07:30.360
for me to introduce you
to a Japanese girl?

00:07:30.360 --> 00:07:31.710
I can't speak Japanese at all.

00:07:31.710 --> 00:07:32.710
I'm going to work.

00:07:34.480 --> 00:07:35.190
Come here, buddy.

00:07:35.190 --> 00:07:37.000
When we are working,

00:07:37.000 --> 00:07:38.530
we must keep the ring clean.

00:07:38.920 --> 00:07:41.430
And the tables and chairs

00:07:41.430 --> 00:07:43.040
must be arranged neatly.

00:07:45.040 --> 00:07:46.570
If you don't want to use him,

00:07:46.820 --> 00:07:49.080
why did you let him
come to the boxing gym?

00:07:50.560 --> 00:07:51.560
It's just that...

00:07:52.560 --> 00:07:54.070
he's from my hometown.

00:07:55.360 --> 00:07:57.890
It's hard to survive in a foreign country.

00:07:58.920 --> 00:08:01.280
I just wanted to help him out.

00:08:02.170 --> 00:08:03.680
Mr. Watanabe,

00:08:03.710 --> 00:08:05.600
if you don't think
he's suitable to stay here,

00:08:05.600 --> 00:08:07.000
I can let him go right now.

00:08:08.630 --> 00:08:11.240
Use Maeda's championship belt
to build the gym's reputation

00:08:11.240 --> 00:08:13.840
and get the financing done
as soon as possible.

00:08:14.120 --> 00:08:16.790
This is our priority.

00:08:18.600 --> 00:08:19.310
I

00:08:19.750 --> 00:08:21.120
have found another job

00:08:21.120 --> 00:08:23.070
at a boxing gym, you know?

00:08:23.480 --> 00:08:24.480
A boxing gym?

00:08:24.920 --> 00:08:26.480
What do you do there?

00:08:26.480 --> 00:08:27.480
Just cleaning up here and there.

00:08:27.480 --> 00:08:28.540
I work as a cleaner.

00:08:28.560 --> 00:08:29.800
And when customers come,

00:08:29.800 --> 00:08:30.830
I work as a waiter.

00:08:31.230 --> 00:08:32.159
The best part is,

00:08:32.600 --> 00:08:34.909
it pays by the hour.

00:08:35.270 --> 00:08:36.480
And I get paid daily.

00:08:36.799 --> 00:08:38.200
Sometimes I even get tips.

00:08:38.200 --> 00:08:40.080
With this job,

00:08:40.320 --> 00:08:42.510
plus the restaurant job,

00:08:43.270 --> 00:08:44.870
I'm making double the money.

00:08:44.870 --> 00:08:46.270
Then I can come find you sooner.

00:08:46.270 --> 00:08:47.870
I want you to come sooner too.

00:08:48.120 --> 00:08:50.050
But you need to take care of yourself too.

00:08:50.050 --> 00:08:51.720
Don't push yourself too hard, okay?

00:08:51.720 --> 00:08:53.670
Not at all. I'm super motivated right now.

00:08:53.670 --> 00:08:54.550
How are things with you?

00:08:54.550 --> 00:08:56.680
Are you busy with your studies lately?

00:08:57.810 --> 00:09:00.360
I've been working on
a catenary structure recently.

00:09:00.360 --> 00:09:01.290
Working on what?

00:09:01.360 --> 00:09:02.690
A catenary structure.

00:09:03.920 --> 00:09:05.410
Catenary structure?

00:09:05.960 --> 00:09:06.770
What is that?

00:09:08.240 --> 00:09:09.150
Xiaoman, I can't talk anymore.

00:09:09.150 --> 00:09:10.350
My classmate is here.

00:09:10.680 --> 00:09:11.270
Okay, okay.

00:09:11.270 --> 00:09:12.730
That's fine. You go ahead.

00:09:13.030 --> 00:09:13.560
Miss you.

00:09:13.860 --> 00:09:14.670
Me too.

00:09:40.120 --> 00:09:41.320
Stop, stop, stop!

00:09:41.600 --> 00:09:42.730
Xiaoman, come here.

00:09:45.840 --> 00:09:48.240
Given your stance, you've trained before?

00:09:48.260 --> 00:09:49.120
Not formally.

00:09:49.120 --> 00:09:52.050
I just learned a bit from my brother
when I was little.

00:09:53.550 --> 00:09:54.080
I see.

00:09:55.080 --> 00:09:56.550
Besides cleaning the venue,

00:09:56.550 --> 00:09:58.010
I'll give you another job.

00:09:58.060 --> 00:09:59.520
Come to my boxing gym
as a sparring partner.

00:09:59.520 --> 00:10:00.250
How about it?

00:10:00.440 --> 00:10:01.320
A full-time sparring partner?

00:10:01.320 --> 00:10:01.790
Yes.

00:10:02.390 --> 00:10:03.960
I'm afraid I'm not up to it.

00:10:03.960 --> 00:10:05.440
You can do it. No problem.

00:10:05.440 --> 00:10:06.630
Then... what about my cleaning job?

00:10:06.630 --> 00:10:08.960
You don't need to do the cleaning anymore.

00:10:10.960 --> 00:10:12.120
Let me tell you,

00:10:12.510 --> 00:10:14.790
being a sparring partner pays

00:10:14.790 --> 00:10:16.630
several times more per hour than cleaning.

00:10:16.630 --> 00:10:17.390
Several times more?

00:10:17.390 --> 00:10:17.960
Yeah.

00:10:17.960 --> 00:10:19.090
Will you do it or not?

00:10:19.440 --> 00:10:20.600
Several times...

00:10:20.810 --> 00:10:22.000
Will you do it or not?

00:10:22.630 --> 00:10:23.080
Will you?

00:10:23.080 --> 00:10:23.790
Okay, okay, okay.

00:10:23.790 --> 00:10:24.320
Do you want to make money?

00:10:24.320 --> 00:10:24.790
Yes, yes, yes.

00:10:24.790 --> 00:10:25.910
Go if you want to make money.

00:10:25.910 --> 00:10:27.170
I'll pay you for today.

00:10:27.200 --> 00:10:27.750
I can get paid for today?

00:10:27.750 --> 00:10:28.150
Right.

00:10:28.150 --> 00:10:28.550
Okay!

00:10:28.630 --> 00:10:29.360
Okay, Yu!

00:10:32.270 --> 00:10:34.200
I envy you and your boyfriend.

00:10:34.320 --> 00:10:35.810
You can see each other whenever you want.

00:10:35.810 --> 00:10:38.260
Are you talking about Leon or Allen?

00:10:40.460 --> 00:10:42.060
The one you met must be Leon.

00:10:42.080 --> 00:10:45.410
That was 3 months ago. Ancient history.

00:10:46.960 --> 00:10:49.870
I broke up with Allen
the day before yesterday.

00:10:52.360 --> 00:10:53.120
I'm sorry.

00:10:54.860 --> 00:11:01.070
Would you give up crêpes for a soufflé?

00:11:02.550 --> 00:11:06.870
There are still croissants and macarons
waiting.

00:11:07.790 --> 00:11:10.790
"You can't give up the whole forest
for a single tree."

00:11:11.070 --> 00:11:12.740
That's a Chinese proverb?

00:11:14.630 --> 00:11:16.480
You see, the two most romantic cultures
in the East and the West

00:11:16.480 --> 00:11:17.960
share the same values.

00:11:18.670 --> 00:11:19.480
That's a joke.

00:11:19.750 --> 00:11:22.160
The true Chinese romance is,

00:11:22.200 --> 00:11:24.480
"Weak water three thousand,
only take one scoop."

00:11:24.480 --> 00:11:27.270
That's classical romance.

00:11:27.600 --> 00:11:28.410
You have it too.

00:11:28.410 --> 00:11:30.170
Don't you have the Little Prince?

00:11:30.170 --> 00:11:32.570
The Little Prince traveled the whole world

00:11:32.840 --> 00:11:33.740
and found that in the world,

00:11:33.740 --> 00:11:35.270
there are many, many roses.

00:11:35.270 --> 00:11:37.630
But he still only loved his one rose.

00:11:37.910 --> 00:11:39.600
And that rose,

00:11:39.600 --> 00:11:41.240
because she received
the Little Prince's love,

00:11:41.240 --> 00:11:42.100
became unique.

00:11:44.440 --> 00:11:48.320
The Little Prince left the rose
to travel the world.

00:11:48.320 --> 00:11:51.750
While he watched sunrises and sunsets
and made friends,

00:11:52.060 --> 00:11:54.970
no one watered the rose.

00:11:54.990 --> 00:12:00.870
She withered while waiting.

00:12:07.930 --> 00:12:09.770
Oh my. Is the phone ringing?

00:12:11.140 --> 00:12:12.360
Here, help me hold this.

00:12:12.360 --> 00:12:13.000
The phone is ringing.

00:12:13.000 --> 00:12:13.840
Maybe the phone is ringing.

00:12:13.840 --> 00:12:14.510
Who is calling?

00:12:14.510 --> 00:12:15.030
Oh my.

00:12:16.690 --> 00:12:17.350
Look at you.

00:12:23.130 --> 00:12:24.330
Whose number is this?

00:12:27.360 --> 00:12:27.750
What...

00:12:27.750 --> 00:12:28.950
Whose number is this?

00:12:29.080 --> 00:12:30.120
Try answering it.

00:12:31.510 --> 00:12:32.030
Hello?

00:12:32.030 --> 00:12:32.600
Hello?

00:12:33.670 --> 00:12:34.240
Hello?

00:12:34.870 --> 00:12:35.510
Mr. Ding?

00:12:35.640 --> 00:12:36.240
Hello?

00:12:36.270 --> 00:12:36.700
Hello?

00:12:36.750 --> 00:12:37.390
Who's calling my brick phone?

00:12:37.390 --> 00:12:37.750
Hello?

00:12:37.750 --> 00:12:38.680
Hello, Mr. Ding.

00:12:38.780 --> 00:12:40.210
It's me, Xiaoman.

00:12:40.270 --> 00:12:41.120
Xiaoman?

00:12:41.570 --> 00:12:42.090
It's me.

00:12:43.480 --> 00:12:44.760
What are you doing, Mr. Ding?

00:12:44.760 --> 00:12:45.570
Xiaoman.

00:12:46.750 --> 00:12:47.750
How are you and Mrs. Ding?

00:12:47.750 --> 00:12:48.750
I... well, I...

00:12:48.750 --> 00:12:49.630
It's him.

00:12:49.720 --> 00:12:50.270
Mrs. Ding and I...

00:12:50.270 --> 00:12:51.510
are doing fine.

00:12:51.750 --> 00:12:52.480
We are fine.

00:12:52.480 --> 00:12:53.240
I'm fine too.

00:12:53.240 --> 00:12:54.440
Don't worry about us.

00:12:54.600 --> 00:12:55.270
-Oh my.
-Well, you—

00:12:55.270 --> 00:12:55.790
The call actually came through.

00:12:55.790 --> 00:12:56.870
Give me your bank account number.

00:12:56.870 --> 00:12:58.600
I'll wire you money. I made some money.

00:12:58.600 --> 00:12:58.960
No.

00:12:58.960 --> 00:12:59.630
-No. No.
-You gave me money secretly.

00:12:59.630 --> 00:13:00.320
No need to wire me money.

00:13:00.320 --> 00:13:00.790
No, no, no. I don't want it.

00:13:00.790 --> 00:13:01.600
I'm wiring it back to you, Mr. Ding.

00:13:01.600 --> 00:13:02.030
No.

00:13:02.030 --> 00:13:02.960
He wants to wire us money.

00:13:02.960 --> 00:13:03.750
No, don't.

00:13:03.750 --> 00:13:04.790
Xiaoman, no, don't wire it.

00:13:04.790 --> 00:13:05.480
Don't wire it. If you do,

00:13:05.480 --> 00:13:06.200
we won't withdraw it.

00:13:06.200 --> 00:13:06.910
We won't withdraw it.

00:13:06.910 --> 00:13:07.750
Alright, let's not talk about this.

00:13:07.750 --> 00:13:08.550
That's it then.

00:13:08.550 --> 00:13:09.680
Don't wire us money.

00:13:09.910 --> 00:13:11.510
I don't need money here, Mr. Ding.

00:13:11.510 --> 00:13:12.360
Are you doing fine?

00:13:12.360 --> 00:13:13.270
Everything is fine.

00:13:13.270 --> 00:13:15.840
-I just miss you both.
-Don't criticize the kid.

00:13:15.840 --> 00:13:17.100
I really miss you both.

00:13:18.600 --> 00:13:19.320
Xiaoman.

00:13:19.500 --> 00:13:20.360
I'm hanging up.

00:13:21.150 --> 00:13:22.210
Why did you hang up?

00:13:26.280 --> 00:13:28.940
You must have memorized
these documents by now.

00:13:29.480 --> 00:13:31.910
This is my first time
working on such a big project.

00:13:31.910 --> 00:13:32.550
I...

00:13:33.150 --> 00:13:34.550
I want to go over them again.

00:13:34.550 --> 00:13:35.630
I'll memorize every detail.

00:13:35.630 --> 00:13:37.840
I want to ensure there are no slip-ups.

00:13:39.600 --> 00:13:40.320
Come in.

00:13:42.630 --> 00:13:43.150
We're here today

00:13:43.150 --> 00:13:44.510
-to see how sincere Fenlier can be.
-Ms. Meng.

00:13:44.510 --> 00:13:45.200
We finally meet.

00:13:45.200 --> 00:13:47.060
We're not begging to be acquired.

00:13:47.080 --> 00:13:48.740
You must be Chief Yang, right?

00:13:49.440 --> 00:13:49.960
Hello.

00:13:50.080 --> 00:13:51.240
I am Meng Ge from Fenlier Group's

00:13:51.240 --> 00:13:52.670
Strategic Investment Department.

00:13:52.670 --> 00:13:54.270
Thank you for making this connection.

00:13:54.270 --> 00:13:55.600
It gave us the chance

00:13:55.600 --> 00:13:58.510
to cooperate deeply with
Jiangnan No. 2 Agricultural Machinery Factory.

00:13:58.510 --> 00:14:00.040
Driving local economic development

00:14:00.040 --> 00:14:02.360
and introducing quality
foreign-funded enterprises like yours

00:14:02.360 --> 00:14:03.760
are the right thing to do.

00:14:05.610 --> 00:14:07.010
No need for formalities.

00:14:10.000 --> 00:14:11.730
You must be Director Li, right?

00:14:12.750 --> 00:14:13.680
You must be Meng.

00:14:14.070 --> 00:14:16.030
I heard that college students
from Shanghai

00:14:16.030 --> 00:14:17.030
are impressive.

00:14:17.360 --> 00:14:18.480
After I meet you today,

00:14:18.480 --> 00:14:19.340
I see it's true.

00:14:19.960 --> 00:14:20.890
You're too kind.

00:14:21.840 --> 00:14:22.750
This is my colleague,

00:14:22.750 --> 00:14:23.360
Xia Lei.

00:14:24.380 --> 00:14:25.390
Hello, Director Li.

00:14:25.390 --> 00:14:25.910
Hello.

00:14:26.670 --> 00:14:27.390
Have a seat.

00:14:27.930 --> 00:14:28.530
By the way,

00:14:29.080 --> 00:14:30.380
let me introduce someone else.

00:14:30.380 --> 00:14:30.900
This

00:14:30.930 --> 00:14:33.560
is the Financial Director
of Jiangnan No. 2 Agricultural Machinery Factory,

00:14:33.560 --> 00:14:34.370
Zhao Chuanhe.

00:14:34.870 --> 00:14:35.510
Welcome, both of you.

00:14:35.510 --> 00:14:36.630
Welcome, both of you.

00:14:36.630 --> 00:14:37.200
Hello.

00:14:37.600 --> 00:14:38.910
Welcome, welcome.

00:14:39.670 --> 00:14:41.080
From your accents,

00:14:41.080 --> 00:14:42.870
you don't sound like Shanghai locals.

00:14:42.870 --> 00:14:43.870
I'm from Beijing.

00:14:43.870 --> 00:14:45.200
I'm from the Northeast.

00:14:46.200 --> 00:14:47.530
Where in the Northeast?

00:14:47.930 --> 00:14:49.720
I was born in Heilongjiang

00:14:49.720 --> 00:14:52.430
and grew up at the East Chemical Plant
in Tiecheng.

00:14:52.430 --> 00:14:53.830
It was a third-tier city.

00:14:54.570 --> 00:14:55.510
It was a Third Front Plant,

00:14:55.510 --> 00:14:56.270
not a third-tier city.

00:14:56.270 --> 00:14:57.470
Look how nervous I am.

00:14:57.920 --> 00:14:59.520
Ah, the East Chemical Plant.

00:15:00.670 --> 00:15:02.080
Back during the technical innovation,

00:15:02.080 --> 00:15:04.480
they invited our engineers and experts

00:15:04.480 --> 00:15:06.480
to go there and share their experience.

00:15:06.480 --> 00:15:07.440
You know

00:15:07.750 --> 00:15:09.000
Chief Chu, right?

00:15:09.240 --> 00:15:10.150
I-I don't know.

00:15:10.440 --> 00:15:11.910
I think there is someone like that.

00:15:11.910 --> 00:15:12.770
I remember him.

00:15:13.030 --> 00:15:15.290
He came to my house
for a New Year's visit.

00:15:15.360 --> 00:15:18.020
Then your parents
must have been plant leaders?

00:15:18.230 --> 00:15:19.560
My dad was the Plant Director.

00:15:19.560 --> 00:15:21.280
Look, now we're talking.

00:15:21.310 --> 00:15:22.900
We're getting closer.

00:15:23.120 --> 00:15:24.030
Come on. Come on.

00:15:24.030 --> 00:15:24.600
Let's drink. Let's drink.

00:15:24.600 --> 00:15:25.330
Director Li,

00:15:25.790 --> 00:15:26.840
our Fenlier Group values

00:15:26.840 --> 00:15:28.630
Jiangnan No. 2 Agricultural Machinery Factory
very highly.

00:15:28.630 --> 00:15:29.430
Rest assured.

00:15:29.670 --> 00:15:31.530
Whether in assets or technology,

00:15:31.550 --> 00:15:33.550
we guarantee a very fair valuation.

00:15:36.150 --> 00:15:36.840
Meng.

00:15:37.360 --> 00:15:38.270
I am

00:15:38.790 --> 00:15:40.030
a straight shooter.

00:15:40.840 --> 00:15:42.040
I just want to ask you,

00:15:42.240 --> 00:15:43.370
in our partnership,

00:15:43.870 --> 00:15:45.310
who will get the fish head,

00:15:45.310 --> 00:15:46.980
and who will get the bones.

00:15:50.720 --> 00:15:51.450
Director Li,

00:15:52.270 --> 00:15:53.960
I'll be honest with you too.

00:15:54.160 --> 00:15:55.570
Jiangnan No. 2 Agricultural Machinery Factory

00:15:55.570 --> 00:15:57.870
is not the only choice
for our Fenlier Group.

00:15:57.870 --> 00:15:59.480
If we just wanted to buy any factory,

00:15:59.480 --> 00:16:01.340
it wouldn't have taken this long.

00:16:10.390 --> 00:16:12.650
Director Li, why don't you think it over?

00:16:12.670 --> 00:16:13.800
I need to take a call.

00:16:29.190 --> 00:16:31.620
Li, Fenlier is a big company,

00:16:32.470 --> 00:16:33.730
and they are very busy.

00:16:34.600 --> 00:16:36.600
Ms. Meng just said

00:16:37.440 --> 00:16:39.870
that we aren't their only target.

00:16:40.710 --> 00:16:43.390
I think joining forces is a good thing,

00:16:43.670 --> 00:16:45.330
but as for the specific terms,

00:16:45.960 --> 00:16:47.390
we still need to talk them through.

00:16:47.390 --> 00:16:48.390
We don't just have

00:16:48.820 --> 00:16:51.500
the option of a joint venture.

00:16:53.550 --> 00:16:54.310
Chief Yang.

00:16:54.870 --> 00:16:56.960
Didn't you tell me last time

00:16:57.870 --> 00:17:01.510
that the government
could help us coordinate a loan?

00:17:01.910 --> 00:17:04.720
Yes, but it's complicated.

00:17:06.000 --> 00:17:06.690
Well...

00:17:09.200 --> 00:17:11.310
Can I say a few words?

00:17:12.069 --> 00:17:14.640
If a loan could solve all problems,

00:17:14.680 --> 00:17:16.640
I don't think there would be

00:17:16.880 --> 00:17:18.810
any entrepreneurs left in this world.

00:17:18.810 --> 00:17:21.109
You surely can ask the bank
for more loans,

00:17:21.109 --> 00:17:23.160
but is money all you lack?

00:17:23.750 --> 00:17:26.069
You started from scratch
with your eight guardians

00:17:26.069 --> 00:17:27.960
and built this business empire.

00:17:27.960 --> 00:17:29.240
It's truly impressive.

00:17:29.240 --> 00:17:30.480
I really admire you.

00:17:31.680 --> 00:17:33.640
But can they keep up with the times?

00:17:33.880 --> 00:17:36.000
Do they understand
modern corporate management

00:17:36.000 --> 00:17:37.720
and the latest technology?

00:17:37.720 --> 00:17:41.880
I remain skeptical about that.

00:17:42.240 --> 00:17:43.370
To be honest,

00:17:44.440 --> 00:17:45.580
now, we need

00:17:45.600 --> 00:17:48.480
funds to transform

00:17:48.720 --> 00:17:51.240
and guarantee basic benefits
for our employees.

00:17:51.240 --> 00:17:55.480
I want to grow this business
and make money,

00:17:55.920 --> 00:17:58.440
but I want to protect
our independent brand even more.

00:17:58.440 --> 00:18:00.750
If anyone tries to take advantage of it,

00:18:02.830 --> 00:18:04.030
I won't stand for it.

00:18:10.610 --> 00:18:11.340
Director Li,

00:18:12.200 --> 00:18:14.660
the No. 2 Agricultural Machinery Factory
is your life's work.

00:18:14.660 --> 00:18:16.400
You've never been willing to give it up.

00:18:16.400 --> 00:18:18.200
As a child of the Third Front Plant,

00:18:18.200 --> 00:18:19.830
I understand this very well.

00:18:20.440 --> 00:18:21.310
We at Fenlier

00:18:21.640 --> 00:18:24.160
sincerely want to cooperate with you.

00:18:30.030 --> 00:18:31.090
Please believe me.

00:18:31.840 --> 00:18:35.750
A joint venture is the best way
for a win-win situation.

00:18:44.680 --> 00:18:45.940
I'll have another one.

00:18:46.070 --> 00:18:46.680
Well...

00:18:51.840 --> 00:18:53.040
I'll finish this pot.

00:18:53.430 --> 00:18:56.630
This shows our sincerity.

00:18:57.160 --> 00:18:57.820
Sincerity.

00:19:23.030 --> 00:19:24.510
You're like a brother to me now.

00:19:24.510 --> 00:19:25.160
Okay. Come on.

00:19:25.160 --> 00:19:26.030
-Let's drink.
-Well done, young man.

00:19:26.030 --> 00:19:27.200
Cheers. Bottoms up.

00:19:28.680 --> 00:19:30.030
Director Li, rest assured.

00:19:30.030 --> 00:19:31.720
Although I'm mainly
in charge of negotiations,

00:19:31.720 --> 00:19:33.920
there is one thing you can be sure of.

00:19:34.160 --> 00:19:36.830
Fenlier doesn't just
solve financial problems;

00:19:36.830 --> 00:19:39.240
we will also inject
tangible resources into the factory,

00:19:39.240 --> 00:19:42.320
upgrade and renovate
existing production lines,

00:19:42.390 --> 00:19:44.740
and provide the best sales team.

00:19:45.160 --> 00:19:46.310
That's great.

00:19:46.310 --> 00:19:47.790
As soon as we make a profit,

00:19:48.000 --> 00:19:49.640
everyone gets a share.

00:19:49.820 --> 00:19:52.220
It's written very clearly in our contract.

00:19:52.680 --> 00:19:53.960
Then our partnership is sure

00:19:53.960 --> 00:19:54.750
to achieve great things.

00:19:54.750 --> 00:19:55.830
Yes, Director Li.

00:19:55.830 --> 00:19:57.720
Sorry, I'm late.

00:19:58.400 --> 00:20:00.160
Meng, where have you been?

00:20:00.640 --> 00:20:01.500
Let me tell you,

00:20:01.590 --> 00:20:02.840
Xia has just shown us

00:20:03.030 --> 00:20:04.400
the utmost sincerity

00:20:04.400 --> 00:20:06.790
of Fenlier!

00:20:06.790 --> 00:20:07.680
Yes, yes, yes.

00:20:08.070 --> 00:20:08.510
You.

00:20:08.750 --> 00:20:09.750
Come here. Hurry.

00:20:09.830 --> 00:20:10.640
No, I can't.

00:20:16.350 --> 00:20:17.830
Come on, man.

00:20:18.070 --> 00:20:18.480
I can't.

00:20:18.480 --> 00:20:19.680
I-I can only hold these.

00:20:19.680 --> 00:20:20.540
I can only spar.

00:20:21.030 --> 00:20:22.310
Spar. Just spar.

00:20:22.510 --> 00:20:23.000
Hurry up. Go.

00:20:23.000 --> 00:20:23.510
But...

00:20:23.590 --> 00:20:25.310
I'm not allowed to wear gloves.

00:20:25.310 --> 00:20:26.570
Says who? I say you can.

00:20:26.590 --> 00:20:28.450
Come on, listen to me. Pick a pair.

00:20:31.680 --> 00:20:32.880
How should I fight, bro?

00:20:32.880 --> 00:20:33.740
Just let loose.

00:20:34.310 --> 00:20:34.750
Let loose?

00:20:34.750 --> 00:20:35.210
Come on.

00:20:35.310 --> 00:20:35.750
Okay.

00:20:36.680 --> 00:20:37.270
Move.

00:20:41.930 --> 00:20:43.170
What happened?

00:20:43.680 --> 00:20:44.400
Are you okay?

00:20:44.400 --> 00:20:45.070
Wake up!

00:20:45.960 --> 00:20:47.030
He passed out!

00:20:47.960 --> 00:20:48.660
That was brutal!

00:20:48.660 --> 00:20:49.720
That was too harsh!

00:20:49.750 --> 00:20:51.550
How could Zhang Xiaoman do this?

00:20:51.830 --> 00:20:53.090
What is wrong with you?

00:20:53.440 --> 00:20:54.590
Is this how you spar?

00:20:55.830 --> 00:20:57.030
Get up, hurry. Get up.

00:20:57.920 --> 00:20:58.720
It's your first time fighting.

00:20:58.720 --> 00:21:00.350
You can't just hit so recklessly.

00:21:00.350 --> 00:21:01.830
If you hurt him badly,

00:21:02.200 --> 00:21:04.000
-you'll ruin his career!
-No, I…

00:21:04.440 --> 00:21:05.770
Alright, stop talking!

00:21:06.070 --> 00:21:06.930
What happened?

00:21:09.840 --> 00:21:10.700
Zhang Xiaoman.

00:21:10.960 --> 00:21:11.560
Come here.

00:21:13.510 --> 00:21:14.750
What's wrong with him?

00:21:14.750 --> 00:21:15.790
Yu, Yu, I was wrong.

00:21:15.790 --> 00:21:17.200
Don't tell me that yet.

00:21:17.350 --> 00:21:18.240
What happened?

00:21:18.270 --> 00:21:20.400
He wanted someone to spar with.

00:21:20.400 --> 00:21:21.960
Then I hit him

00:21:21.960 --> 00:21:23.200
right on his chin

00:21:24.710 --> 00:21:25.780
and knocked him out.

00:21:25.780 --> 00:21:26.890
Did you wear gloves?

00:21:26.890 --> 00:21:27.370
Yes.

00:21:27.400 --> 00:21:28.600
He made you wear them?

00:21:29.960 --> 00:21:31.200
Are you the sparring partner,

00:21:31.200 --> 00:21:32.470
or is he?

00:21:32.470 --> 00:21:33.240
I won't wear them anymore.

00:21:33.240 --> 00:21:33.750
Let me tell you something.

00:21:33.750 --> 00:21:36.000
He's been training
at our club for almost 3 years.

00:21:36.000 --> 00:21:37.350
If you injure him,

00:21:37.350 --> 00:21:38.790
who's going to compete in his place?

00:21:38.790 --> 00:21:39.830
You?

00:21:39.830 --> 00:21:41.000
I-I can't.

00:21:46.540 --> 00:21:47.150
Xiaoman.

00:21:47.170 --> 00:21:47.650
Yu.

00:21:48.410 --> 00:21:50.720
Have you ever thought about entering

00:21:52.000 --> 00:21:53.070
an amateur match?

00:21:53.200 --> 00:21:54.070
I-I can't.

00:21:54.070 --> 00:21:55.440
I only know how to throw a punch.

00:21:55.440 --> 00:21:57.100
I don't understand the rules.

00:21:57.240 --> 00:21:58.440
The rules are simple.

00:21:58.830 --> 00:22:00.490
I'll find a coach to train you,

00:22:00.960 --> 00:22:01.510
okay?

00:22:02.350 --> 00:22:03.410
And let me tell you,

00:22:03.750 --> 00:22:04.880
there's money in it.

00:22:06.160 --> 00:22:07.440
As long as you participate in a match,

00:22:07.440 --> 00:22:09.070
win or lose, you get paid.

00:22:09.070 --> 00:22:09.880
If you win,

00:22:10.160 --> 00:22:11.160
you get even more.

00:22:11.400 --> 00:22:12.110
You in?

00:22:13.440 --> 00:22:14.440
How much more?

00:22:14.440 --> 00:22:15.550
A lot more.

00:22:17.270 --> 00:22:18.200
Think it over.

00:22:18.640 --> 00:22:19.070
Okay.

00:22:19.640 --> 00:22:21.170
Let me know when you decide.

00:22:22.510 --> 00:22:24.960
Sign this project document.

00:22:26.590 --> 00:22:28.200
After the company confirms it,

00:22:28.200 --> 00:22:32.550
we'll start drafting the contract
for the No. 2 Agricultural Machinery Factory.

00:22:32.550 --> 00:22:33.960
By the way, after the signing,

00:22:33.960 --> 00:22:35.220
you should sign it too.

00:22:36.590 --> 00:22:37.920
My probation period isn't over yet.

00:22:37.920 --> 00:22:39.200
It's inappropriate, isn't it?

00:22:39.200 --> 00:22:41.270
You'll be a full employee
after this project.

00:22:41.270 --> 00:22:43.640
Besides, you deserve the most credit
for this negotiation.

00:22:43.640 --> 00:22:44.320
Sign it.

00:22:52.720 --> 00:22:55.550
Our department's performance
is outstanding this time.

00:22:55.550 --> 00:22:56.240
I am

00:22:56.440 --> 00:22:57.830
definitely moving up.

00:22:58.310 --> 00:23:00.310
My position will be open then.

00:23:00.960 --> 00:23:02.870
I hope when the opportunity comes,

00:23:02.870 --> 00:23:03.790
one of you

00:23:04.160 --> 00:23:05.270
can take my place,

00:23:05.640 --> 00:23:06.790
because I have more faith in people

00:23:06.790 --> 00:23:09.000
who have been through the trenches
with me.

00:23:09.000 --> 00:23:10.200
I hope you understand

00:23:10.480 --> 00:23:11.830
what I'm saying.

00:23:13.310 --> 00:23:14.040
Understood.

00:23:14.200 --> 00:23:14.930
Understood.

00:23:15.510 --> 00:23:18.170
Kong Peng asked you
to sign the document just now

00:23:18.350 --> 00:23:19.680
and proposed choosing one of us

00:23:19.680 --> 00:23:21.070
to be the successor.

00:23:21.680 --> 00:23:23.070
Do you understand what he means?

00:23:23.070 --> 00:23:24.720
He wants us to keep each other in check.

00:23:24.720 --> 00:23:26.520
He wants us to turn on each other.

00:23:27.550 --> 00:23:28.400
But remember,

00:23:28.680 --> 00:23:30.880
we must never fight against each other.

00:23:31.550 --> 00:23:34.440
And don't forget,
you still owe me a favor.

00:23:34.600 --> 00:23:36.110
Then I'll admit defeat right now.

00:23:36.110 --> 00:23:37.510
For the sake of us being old classmates,

00:23:37.510 --> 00:23:38.790
please go easy on me.

00:23:38.790 --> 00:23:41.350
I'm willing to be your gofer

00:23:41.350 --> 00:23:41.960
for life.

00:23:42.200 --> 00:23:43.680
Have some ambition.

00:23:44.000 --> 00:23:46.200
I was joking. Did you take it seriously?

00:23:46.640 --> 00:23:47.750
After entering the real world,

00:23:47.750 --> 00:23:48.550
I realized

00:23:48.830 --> 00:23:50.030
that many principles

00:23:50.160 --> 00:23:52.270
are completely different
from what we learned in books.

00:23:52.270 --> 00:23:53.400
But no matter what,

00:23:53.680 --> 00:23:55.140
even if it's just for show,

00:23:55.160 --> 00:23:57.290
you must act like you can stand up to me.

00:23:57.830 --> 00:23:58.680
It benefits us both.

00:23:58.680 --> 00:24:00.140
We rise and fall together.

00:24:08.240 --> 00:24:09.100
Do you believe?

00:24:10.030 --> 00:24:13.070
I'll surely have a place here
in the future.

00:24:14.450 --> 00:24:15.290
I will too.

00:24:19.580 --> 00:24:20.100
Stop!

00:24:23.740 --> 00:24:24.500
Finish!

00:24:37.400 --> 00:24:38.110
Xiaoman.

00:24:39.960 --> 00:24:41.030
It's your turn.

00:24:43.880 --> 00:24:45.280
Are you a little nervous?

00:24:45.680 --> 00:24:47.960
It's okay. Everyone has a first time.

00:24:49.070 --> 00:24:50.470
Just think of it this way.

00:24:51.880 --> 00:24:55.350
Treat it
like your usual sparring sessions.

00:24:55.830 --> 00:24:58.490
You'd get hit in the body and face,
wouldn't you?

00:24:59.790 --> 00:25:02.160
You'll still take a few hits today.

00:25:02.160 --> 00:25:02.790
But

00:25:03.510 --> 00:25:07.030
today, you can fight back all you want.

00:25:20.200 --> 00:25:20.900
Kid.

00:25:22.510 --> 00:25:25.440
Do you want to get your teeth smashed in
out there?

00:25:26.590 --> 00:25:28.250
You're not even wearing this.

00:25:29.920 --> 00:25:30.830
Look at me.

00:25:31.720 --> 00:25:32.590
Listen to me.

00:25:33.160 --> 00:25:34.310
Don't think about anything.

00:25:34.310 --> 00:25:35.640
All you should think about

00:25:35.640 --> 00:25:36.590
is making money.

00:25:36.770 --> 00:25:39.050
You gotta make money. Big money.

00:25:41.500 --> 00:25:47.140
♪ I've walked through dark alleys, hit
against high walls, fallen into the pond ♪

00:25:47.360 --> 00:25:49.590
♪ I've pursued my ideals, hated this body,
and been to the middle of nowhere ♪

00:25:49.590 --> 00:25:53.920
Xiaoman! Xiaoman! Xiaoman!

00:25:53.920 --> 00:25:59.150
♪ Gazing at the moon in a foreign land
in the gap of the city ♪

00:25:59.310 --> 00:26:03.560
♪ Wishing only for the credit of one
who has crossed the bridge ♪

00:26:04.750 --> 00:26:05.480
Xiaoman! Xiaoman! Xiaoman!

00:26:05.480 --> 00:26:08.130
♪ Look at the river flowing ♪

00:26:08.160 --> 00:26:11.540
♪ Where will the young man
on the bridge go? ♪

00:26:11.570 --> 00:26:14.360
♪ The vibrant spring sees flying birds
and thriving greenery ♪

00:26:14.380 --> 00:26:16.920
♪ But my heart remains the same ♪

00:26:17.460 --> 00:26:21.350
♪ Listen to the wuthering wind
in the fog ♪

00:26:21.380 --> 00:26:23.610
♪ The one crossing the bridge
has no fear of the road ahead ♪

00:26:23.630 --> 00:26:24.940
♪ With the figure fading away ♪

00:26:25.030 --> 00:26:27.450
♪ The reckless youth is gone from now on ♪

00:26:27.550 --> 00:26:29.830
Xiaoman! Come on! Xiaoman!

00:26:29.850 --> 00:26:32.320
♪ Look at the river flowing ♪

00:26:32.360 --> 00:26:35.510
♪ Where will the young man
on the bridge go? ♪

00:26:35.560 --> 00:26:37.310
♪ The vibrant spring sees flying birds
and thriving greenery ♪

00:26:37.310 --> 00:26:38.370
Xiaoman! Xiaoman! Xiaoman!

00:26:38.370 --> 00:26:40.910
♪ But my heart remains the same ♪

00:26:41.450 --> 00:26:43.590
♪ Listen to the wuthering wind
in the fog ♪

00:26:43.590 --> 00:26:45.350
The winner is Zhang Xiaoman!

00:26:45.370 --> 00:26:45.640
♪ The one crossing the bridge
has no fear of the road ahead ♪

00:26:45.640 --> 00:26:46.240
KO!

00:26:46.440 --> 00:26:47.620
Xiaoman! Xiaoman! Xiaoman!

00:26:47.620 --> 00:26:48.930
♪ With the figure fading away ♪

00:26:49.020 --> 00:26:51.440
♪ The reckless youth is gone from now on ♪

00:26:53.630 --> 00:26:55.170
♪ With the figure fading away ♪

00:26:55.190 --> 00:26:57.540
♪ The reckless youth is gone from now on ♪

00:26:57.590 --> 00:27:00.160
Miss Yamaomo, can I help you?

00:27:01.740 --> 00:27:04.470
Who is that new guy?

00:27:05.640 --> 00:27:08.120
He's a sparring partner at our boxing gym.

00:27:11.070 --> 00:27:14.030
I think he has a lot of potential.

00:27:14.840 --> 00:27:17.370
It's a waste to keep him
as a sparring partner.

00:27:17.750 --> 00:27:19.280
I understand what you mean.

00:27:19.640 --> 00:27:20.770
I'm counting on you.

00:27:27.550 --> 00:27:29.720
You know that family's status.

00:27:30.640 --> 00:27:32.110
Since she's interested in Zhang Xiaoman

00:27:32.110 --> 00:27:33.640
and willing to fund the gym,

00:27:34.440 --> 00:27:35.920
forget about Maeda for now.

00:27:35.920 --> 00:27:38.650
Use Zhang Xiaoman
and have him fight more fights.

00:27:39.510 --> 00:27:40.770
For the sake of the gym,

00:27:40.790 --> 00:27:42.920
you have to make good use of this pawn.

00:27:43.000 --> 00:27:43.590
Okay.

00:27:44.320 --> 00:27:45.320
I got it.

00:27:46.310 --> 00:27:47.110
Xiaoman.

00:27:47.650 --> 00:27:48.210
Yu.

00:27:49.590 --> 00:27:51.980
You were really impressive today.

00:27:52.270 --> 00:27:54.830
You knocked him out with just a few hits.

00:27:56.920 --> 00:27:59.270
That fighter has been training
for 3 years,

00:27:59.270 --> 00:28:01.510
and is preparing to go pro.

00:28:01.640 --> 00:28:04.040
You made a name for yourself
by beating him.

00:28:04.460 --> 00:28:06.740
You have the potential to be a boxer.

00:28:11.150 --> 00:28:13.550
Here is your prize money
for today's match.

00:28:21.510 --> 00:28:22.200
This...

00:28:22.620 --> 00:28:23.660
this much?

00:28:23.990 --> 00:28:24.920
It's all yours.

00:28:25.830 --> 00:28:26.200
Don't you want it?

00:28:26.200 --> 00:28:27.310
Why is it so much?

00:28:27.440 --> 00:28:28.680
Well, you can give me half if you want.

00:28:28.680 --> 00:28:29.440
Well, Yu.

00:28:29.440 --> 00:28:31.310
Didn't we say
it would only be a few thousand?

00:28:31.310 --> 00:28:32.000
Why is there so much?

00:28:32.000 --> 00:28:33.270
You won.

00:28:33.810 --> 00:28:34.520
Take it.

00:28:35.310 --> 00:28:36.770
This isn't even that much.

00:28:37.350 --> 00:28:38.680
Let's not even talk about
the championship belt.

00:28:38.680 --> 00:28:40.280
You can't fight for that yet.

00:28:40.440 --> 00:28:42.000
If you just join some

00:28:42.000 --> 00:28:43.030
small club matches,

00:28:43.030 --> 00:28:45.110
you'll earn way more than this.

00:28:45.110 --> 00:28:46.480
If you go higher

00:28:47.160 --> 00:28:48.680
and join some medium-sized matches

00:28:48.680 --> 00:28:49.550
or large-scale matches,

00:28:49.550 --> 00:28:50.880
the money will keep growing

00:28:50.880 --> 00:28:51.680
and growing.

00:28:51.840 --> 00:28:53.710
It'll snowball.

00:28:55.640 --> 00:28:58.510
One match pays more than this?

00:28:58.550 --> 00:28:59.400
Of course.

00:29:00.350 --> 00:29:02.550
So, your time has come, kid.

00:29:13.070 --> 00:29:13.830
Hello, Xiaoman?

00:29:13.830 --> 00:29:14.760
Hello, Xiaodan.

00:29:14.860 --> 00:29:16.660
Why are you calling me so late?

00:29:16.830 --> 00:29:18.550
I'm almost done with my first painting.

00:29:18.550 --> 00:29:20.150
I just finished cleaning up.

00:29:20.270 --> 00:29:20.750
Let me tell you,

00:29:20.750 --> 00:29:22.510
I fought in a match today.

00:29:22.950 --> 00:29:24.980
A match? What kind of match?

00:29:25.350 --> 00:29:26.070
At the boxing gym?

00:29:26.070 --> 00:29:27.960
Aren't you a waiter there?

00:29:28.030 --> 00:29:30.550
I started out as a cleaner here.

00:29:30.920 --> 00:29:32.590
Then, our boss

00:29:32.720 --> 00:29:33.880
ran out of sparring partners
the other day,

00:29:33.880 --> 00:29:35.210
so he asked me to step in.

00:29:35.230 --> 00:29:36.860
After sparring for a while,
he realized I wasn't bad.

00:29:36.860 --> 00:29:38.380
He let me try out with them,

00:29:38.410 --> 00:29:40.610
and today he recommended me for a match.

00:29:40.660 --> 00:29:42.100
Did you get hurt?

00:29:42.480 --> 00:29:44.680
I'm fine. Guess if I won?

00:29:46.200 --> 00:29:47.590
Since you're asking me like that,

00:29:47.590 --> 00:29:48.920
you must have won.

00:29:49.160 --> 00:29:49.680
Who would have thought

00:29:49.680 --> 00:29:52.110
what I learned back then
would be useful here?

00:29:52.110 --> 00:29:52.680
Let me tell you,

00:29:52.680 --> 00:29:54.110
what I make in one match

00:29:54.110 --> 00:29:55.880
is way more than my other jobs.

00:29:56.280 --> 00:29:58.170
You're already working two jobs.

00:29:58.590 --> 00:29:59.830
Do you have to box too?

00:29:59.860 --> 00:30:01.580
It's all about the money.

00:30:01.830 --> 00:30:03.160
The faster I earn it,

00:30:03.160 --> 00:30:04.760
the sooner I can come see you.

00:30:04.920 --> 00:30:07.380
But I'm more worried
about you getting hurt.

00:30:09.680 --> 00:30:10.640
The restaurant is calling.

00:30:10.640 --> 00:30:11.400
I have to go.

00:30:11.510 --> 00:30:12.840
I'm heading to work now.

00:30:30.750 --> 00:30:31.680
You're still up?

00:30:34.030 --> 00:30:35.090
You know how to box?

00:30:36.440 --> 00:30:37.750
You watched my match?

00:30:38.400 --> 00:30:40.440
You came to Japan to make money,

00:30:40.440 --> 00:30:42.160
not to risk your life.

00:30:43.330 --> 00:30:44.660
I'm not risking my life.

00:30:45.170 --> 00:30:46.610
I'm just messing around.

00:30:48.880 --> 00:30:50.750
You come back so late every day.

00:30:50.750 --> 00:30:52.480
I'm just showing some concern.

00:30:53.160 --> 00:30:53.960
Is that wrong?

00:30:54.420 --> 00:30:55.620
You're right.

00:30:56.030 --> 00:30:57.030
I-I just...

00:30:57.640 --> 00:30:59.110
I just spar with them for fun.

00:30:59.110 --> 00:31:00.000
It's just small-time stuff.

00:31:00.000 --> 00:31:00.720
It's fine.

00:31:00.880 --> 00:31:02.590
It feels easy now,

00:31:03.110 --> 00:31:04.310
but what about later?

00:31:04.510 --> 00:31:07.040
There will be more and more
strong opponents.

00:31:08.030 --> 00:31:11.880
If I had known you could box,

00:31:11.930 --> 00:31:14.390
I never would have sent you
to the boxing gym.

00:31:14.790 --> 00:31:16.520
I didn't plan to fight at first.

00:31:16.830 --> 00:31:18.310
But then they let me try.

00:31:18.310 --> 00:31:19.160
It turned out okay.

00:31:19.160 --> 00:31:20.490
And it pays pretty well.

00:31:20.550 --> 00:31:22.720
I just want to make more money quickly,

00:31:22.720 --> 00:31:24.250
so I can go to France sooner.

00:31:26.270 --> 00:31:30.400
But you are gambling your life and future

00:31:31.310 --> 00:31:32.550
on your dream.

00:31:52.270 --> 00:31:53.800
No one came to eat all night.

00:31:54.590 --> 00:31:57.320
Bought all this meat and vegetables
for nothing.

00:32:01.960 --> 00:32:04.310
How much did we spend on this stuff today?

00:32:07.590 --> 00:32:08.590
I'm asking you.

00:32:08.830 --> 00:32:09.880
Not much.

00:32:18.960 --> 00:32:19.560
Everyone!

00:32:21.440 --> 00:32:22.640
Let me say a few words.

00:32:22.790 --> 00:32:24.640
My apprentice made money in Japan today.

00:32:24.640 --> 00:32:25.440
It's my treat.

00:32:25.590 --> 00:32:28.590
Come try Ding's Chicken Ribs.

00:32:30.110 --> 00:32:31.680
Ding's Grilled Chicken Ribs.

00:32:31.680 --> 00:32:32.590
Come on. Come.

00:32:32.590 --> 00:32:33.830
Why are you still selling clothes?

00:32:33.830 --> 00:32:34.680
Who buys them in the middle of the night?

00:32:34.680 --> 00:32:35.160
Li,

00:32:35.270 --> 00:32:36.880
bring two roasted sweet potatoes.
Let me taste them.

00:32:36.880 --> 00:32:37.880
Hurry up and roast them. Quick.

00:32:37.880 --> 00:32:38.640
Okay, okay.

00:32:38.830 --> 00:32:39.890
This kid. This kid.

00:32:40.070 --> 00:32:41.070
Let's eat. Let's eat!

00:32:41.070 --> 00:32:42.480
Open the beer. What are you doing?

00:32:42.480 --> 00:32:43.210
Spacing out?

00:32:45.070 --> 00:32:45.750
Come on. Come on.

00:32:45.750 --> 00:32:46.920
You drink too. Come on.

00:32:46.920 --> 00:32:47.380
Come on.

00:32:47.880 --> 00:32:49.270
Come on. Let's eat and drink well.

00:32:49.270 --> 00:32:50.680
Life must go on.

00:32:58.070 --> 00:32:59.680
What? Will the sun hide tomorrow

00:32:59.680 --> 00:33:00.830
and not come out?

00:33:03.510 --> 00:33:05.710
Ding, you really are a stand-up guy.

00:33:06.160 --> 00:33:07.290
You know how to live.

00:33:18.560 --> 00:33:19.410
Come on. Cheers.

00:33:19.410 --> 00:33:20.070
What's wrong?

00:33:20.070 --> 00:33:20.720
Nothing.

00:33:21.720 --> 00:33:23.310
Why are you like this? Talk to me.

00:33:23.310 --> 00:33:24.200
Why are you crying?

00:33:24.200 --> 00:33:25.330
The garlic is spicy.

00:33:25.440 --> 00:33:26.240
A scallion is spicy.

00:33:26.240 --> 00:33:27.880
How can garlic burn your eyes?

00:33:27.880 --> 00:33:29.030
Alright, alright.

00:33:29.310 --> 00:33:30.750
Why are you crying in front of people?

00:33:30.750 --> 00:33:31.880
Like I bullied you.

00:33:38.880 --> 00:33:40.140
Give me a kiss. Come on.

00:33:41.310 --> 00:33:43.370
Everyone is here. What are you doing?

00:33:43.510 --> 00:33:44.720
You're my own wife. So what?

00:33:44.720 --> 00:33:46.400
Can't I just kiss you if I want to?

00:33:46.400 --> 00:33:47.590
Shoo, shoo.

00:33:51.030 --> 00:33:52.760
Forget it. Your face is greasy.

00:33:57.030 --> 00:33:59.270
Don't worry.
We've endured all kinds of hardships.

00:33:59.270 --> 00:34:00.730
Do you remember back then?

00:34:01.720 --> 00:34:02.640
Those fish bones had thorns.

00:34:02.640 --> 00:34:04.700
We mashed them up, added some garlic,

00:34:05.310 --> 00:34:07.270
and mixed in some of those
wild vegetable leaves.

00:34:07.270 --> 00:34:08.800
It tasted great, didn't it?

00:34:11.070 --> 00:34:12.469
Just listen to me.

00:34:12.489 --> 00:34:13.280
No matter what happens,

00:34:13.280 --> 00:34:14.710
from now on, let's just

00:34:14.710 --> 00:34:15.920
be happy.

00:34:17.000 --> 00:34:18.199
I'll get back to work.

00:34:18.710 --> 00:34:19.540
Come here.

00:34:26.270 --> 00:34:29.199
Kissing me right on the mouth.
You're wilder than me.

00:34:30.550 --> 00:34:32.080
How much garlic did you eat?

00:34:42.030 --> 00:34:43.560
Come here. Let me introduce you.

00:34:43.560 --> 00:34:44.710
This is Zhang Xiaoman.

00:34:44.710 --> 00:34:46.230
He's from China.

00:34:46.760 --> 00:34:48.630
He'll be your exclusive coach from now on.

00:34:48.630 --> 00:34:50.440
His surname is Chen. He's also from China.

00:34:50.440 --> 00:34:52.070
This isn't appropriate, is it?

00:34:52.070 --> 00:34:53.230
What's inappropriate about it?

00:34:53.230 --> 00:34:54.190
This area

00:34:54.190 --> 00:34:56.190
is your exclusive training ground.

00:34:56.670 --> 00:34:59.560
I only fought one match.

00:34:59.580 --> 00:35:00.710
Yes, it's just one match,

00:35:00.710 --> 00:35:01.960
but you are the future star

00:35:01.960 --> 00:35:03.030
of our club.

00:35:03.440 --> 00:35:05.920
Mr. Watanabe specifically ordered this.

00:35:06.190 --> 00:35:07.840
So, we have high hopes for you.

00:35:07.840 --> 00:35:08.960
Good luck.

00:35:09.030 --> 00:35:09.670
Okay.

00:35:10.070 --> 00:35:11.390
Talk to the coach for a while.

00:35:11.390 --> 00:35:12.060
Sure.

00:35:12.150 --> 00:35:13.750
Find me if you need anything.

00:35:17.440 --> 00:35:19.720
Xiaoman, I watched your match.

00:35:20.150 --> 00:35:22.270
You won because of your explosive power.

00:35:22.270 --> 00:35:23.100
But

00:35:23.410 --> 00:35:25.030
in terms of technique,

00:35:25.030 --> 00:35:26.560
you still need to practice.

00:35:26.880 --> 00:35:29.280
Right. I've never learned before.

00:35:29.280 --> 00:35:31.080
I used to practice with friends.

00:35:36.670 --> 00:35:39.000
Whether it's physical fitness

00:35:39.320 --> 00:35:41.920
or striking power,

00:35:42.480 --> 00:35:44.320
Zhang Xiaoman is one of the best

00:35:44.800 --> 00:35:46.400
among all our club members.

00:35:46.880 --> 00:35:48.510
If we train him well,

00:35:48.710 --> 00:35:50.640
not only will Yamaomo invest in us,

00:35:51.110 --> 00:35:52.910
but the club can also make money.

00:35:54.590 --> 00:35:55.670
In that case,

00:35:56.070 --> 00:35:58.070
make good use of this kid.

00:35:58.400 --> 00:36:00.150
To keep Xiaoman from leaving,

00:36:00.190 --> 00:36:02.280
give him a taste of success.

00:36:02.630 --> 00:36:03.230
Yes.

00:36:03.960 --> 00:36:04.960
Here's a project.

00:36:05.030 --> 00:36:06.030
Take a quick look.

00:36:06.440 --> 00:36:08.470
I was going to send you to investigate,

00:36:08.470 --> 00:36:10.590
but they came to us on their own.

00:36:10.620 --> 00:36:12.170
There will be a meeting in an hour.

00:36:12.170 --> 00:36:14.500
Meet with them after you're done reading.

00:36:14.670 --> 00:36:16.550
Rest assured. I'll handle it.

00:36:17.790 --> 00:36:18.950
For this task,

00:36:18.970 --> 00:36:21.040
I want Xia Lei to lead.

00:36:23.190 --> 00:36:23.800
Why?

00:36:24.440 --> 00:36:26.590
Because your recent performance
has been excellent.

00:36:26.590 --> 00:36:29.050
I think you can handle things
on your own now.

00:36:29.440 --> 00:36:30.040
Of course,

00:36:30.510 --> 00:36:31.760
switching positions

00:36:32.110 --> 00:36:33.590
will be good for both of you.

00:36:33.590 --> 00:36:34.230
But...

00:36:34.820 --> 00:36:37.090
You need to help Xia Lei out this time.

00:36:40.000 --> 00:36:42.660
Hurry up and read.
We have a meeting afterwards.

00:36:42.860 --> 00:36:44.720
There's a lot to go through. Go on.

00:36:57.840 --> 00:36:58.440
See?

00:37:04.550 --> 00:37:06.210
Didn't you say

00:37:06.510 --> 00:37:08.280
the more he wants us to fight,

00:37:08.280 --> 00:37:09.840
the less we should?

00:37:10.190 --> 00:37:11.850
Why are you getting upset now?

00:37:12.550 --> 00:37:14.800
Now I really have to be your assistant.

00:37:15.760 --> 00:37:17.760
Am I not allowed to be a little upset?

00:37:19.430 --> 00:37:22.140
I'll treat you to hotpot tonight, okay?

00:37:24.880 --> 00:37:25.550
Fine.

00:37:26.280 --> 00:37:27.510
Then cheer up.

00:37:30.400 --> 00:37:31.590
Tell me about it,

00:37:31.590 --> 00:37:32.400
Leader.

00:37:32.920 --> 00:37:35.720
What kind of company
is Jiangnan Machinery Plant?

00:37:42.110 --> 00:37:42.910
What's wrong?

00:37:46.660 --> 00:37:48.080
I know this managing director.

00:37:48.080 --> 00:37:49.400
[Managing Director: Fan Weijie]

00:37:49.400 --> 00:37:50.320
Fan Weijie?

00:37:52.630 --> 00:37:54.290
We had some issues in the past.

00:37:55.280 --> 00:37:56.610
But that's all over now.

00:37:59.110 --> 00:37:59.670
Xia Lei,

00:38:00.340 --> 00:38:01.860
I have to tell you this.

00:38:02.710 --> 00:38:04.310
You need to be professional.

00:38:04.400 --> 00:38:06.170
Don't let personal feelings affect work.

00:38:06.170 --> 00:38:06.740
Look,

00:38:07.070 --> 00:38:09.130
Kong Peng made me your assistant now,

00:38:09.550 --> 00:38:11.280
but I'll still do my job well.

00:38:13.610 --> 00:38:14.300
It's fine.

00:38:18.440 --> 00:38:19.840
Have you really decided?

00:38:20.960 --> 00:38:22.630
I want to try, Auntie.

00:38:25.150 --> 00:38:27.440
You're going about this the wrong way.

00:38:28.390 --> 00:38:30.120
It will backfire.

00:38:36.790 --> 00:38:40.150
Look, I've lived for over 20 years,

00:38:40.830 --> 00:38:43.760
and I haven't accomplished a single thing
until now,

00:38:44.050 --> 00:38:45.780
except for this.

00:38:47.070 --> 00:38:47.930
I have a chance.

00:38:49.790 --> 00:38:51.710
You think standing in the ring

00:38:53.070 --> 00:38:54.470
means you've succeeded?

00:38:57.000 --> 00:38:58.060
How should I put it?

00:38:58.510 --> 00:38:59.710
I won my first match.

00:39:00.000 --> 00:39:01.070
And after I won,

00:39:01.070 --> 00:39:02.510
after I knocked that guy out,

00:39:02.510 --> 00:39:03.510
I was in the ring,

00:39:03.710 --> 00:39:05.840
and everyone was screaming for me.

00:39:05.840 --> 00:39:07.500
They were all cheering for me.

00:39:07.510 --> 00:39:09.110
Oh my god, that feeling...

00:39:10.070 --> 00:39:11.200
How do I describe it?

00:39:11.400 --> 00:39:12.330
In my whole life,

00:39:12.590 --> 00:39:14.590
I only felt that once back in school.

00:39:14.710 --> 00:39:16.040
I haven't felt it since.

00:39:16.760 --> 00:39:19.550
So, do you enjoy this feeling of success,

00:39:20.190 --> 00:39:21.800
or is it like you said,

00:39:23.030 --> 00:39:26.430
earning enough money
to go to France to find your girlfriend?

00:39:26.700 --> 00:39:27.230
I...

00:39:27.230 --> 00:39:30.030
My goal is definitely
to earn money to go to France.

00:39:30.590 --> 00:39:32.510
Since I can win at boxing,

00:39:32.510 --> 00:39:33.710
why shouldn't I do it?

00:39:33.760 --> 00:39:35.220
But with a goal like yours,

00:39:35.440 --> 00:39:38.130
it's not pure anymore
with those added motives.

00:39:41.230 --> 00:39:43.160
Actually, my goal hasn't changed,

00:39:43.230 --> 00:39:44.650
but the process

00:39:44.810 --> 00:39:47.050
has changed a little bit.

00:39:47.970 --> 00:39:50.150
My husband, Mr. Maeda,

00:39:51.150 --> 00:39:53.920
fell in the boxing ring.

00:39:55.830 --> 00:39:57.960
He left me a lot of his honors in the end,

00:40:00.050 --> 00:40:02.570
but I don't need those things.

00:40:02.600 --> 00:40:04.120
I need him.

00:40:05.960 --> 00:40:07.880
To make these decisions,

00:40:09.080 --> 00:40:12.610
have you ever considered
the people around you and your family?

00:40:14.760 --> 00:40:18.070
Auntie, it's not that serious.

00:40:18.360 --> 00:40:19.550
I'm not fighting professionally.

00:40:19.550 --> 00:40:21.400
I'm fighting in amateur matches.

00:40:21.400 --> 00:40:23.600
But I'm pretty good in amateur matches.

00:40:24.210 --> 00:40:25.610
Really, I'm quite tough.

00:40:26.360 --> 00:40:27.360
Let me tell you,

00:40:27.880 --> 00:40:30.400
no matter how strong someone is,

00:40:30.800 --> 00:40:34.000
they are ultimately losers in the ring.

00:40:34.510 --> 00:40:35.760
They lose to time,

00:40:36.370 --> 00:40:38.690
and to stronger opponents.

00:40:42.980 --> 00:40:43.790
I... I...

00:40:44.990 --> 00:40:47.960
I'll just fight a few matches.

00:40:47.980 --> 00:40:50.050
I won't make a career out of it.

00:40:50.320 --> 00:40:51.650
Just to make some money.

00:40:54.750 --> 00:40:57.480
You take responsibility
for your own decisions.

00:41:08.000 --> 00:41:08.550
Mr. Fan.

00:41:12.480 --> 00:41:13.360
This is my colleague,

00:41:13.360 --> 00:41:14.480
Manager Meng Ge.

00:41:16.760 --> 00:41:17.620
Hello, Mr. Fan.

00:41:19.880 --> 00:41:20.360
Hello.

00:41:22.230 --> 00:41:23.360
Lei, you work here?

00:41:23.860 --> 00:41:24.860
Let's have a seat.

00:41:26.360 --> 00:41:27.760
Did you know I was coming?

00:41:28.030 --> 00:41:29.960
You didn't even tell me in advance.

00:41:29.960 --> 00:41:30.630
Look at you.

00:41:30.920 --> 00:41:32.510
Mr. Fan, regarding the acquisition,

00:41:32.510 --> 00:41:33.840
if you have any conditions or ideas,

00:41:33.840 --> 00:41:34.840
we can discuss them.

00:41:34.840 --> 00:41:35.590
We can talk however you want.

00:41:35.590 --> 00:41:36.650
Don't be so formal.

00:41:37.110 --> 00:41:38.310
Are you free tonight?

00:41:38.480 --> 00:41:39.760
About that matter...

00:41:39.760 --> 00:41:40.840
let me explain.

00:41:41.630 --> 00:41:43.510
We can talk about the acquisition,

00:41:43.510 --> 00:41:44.190
but if it's personal matters,

00:41:44.190 --> 00:41:45.390
this isn't the place.

00:41:47.110 --> 00:41:49.710
Fine. Let's talk acquisition first.
Go ahead.

00:41:50.280 --> 00:41:50.810
Go ahead.

00:41:51.110 --> 00:41:52.670
Mr. Fan, I'm sorry.

00:41:53.230 --> 00:41:55.110
We just took over this project,

00:41:55.400 --> 00:41:57.660
so we don't know the specifics very well.

00:41:57.670 --> 00:41:59.480
I just took a rough look at the documents.

00:41:59.480 --> 00:42:00.360
Currently, your factory

00:42:00.360 --> 00:42:02.760
can no longer maintain normal production.

00:42:02.760 --> 00:42:04.960
Many orders can't be delivered on time.

00:42:05.510 --> 00:42:06.550
To put it bluntly,

00:42:07.150 --> 00:42:09.550
your factory
is on the verge of bankruptcy.

00:42:10.190 --> 00:42:10.880
Ms. Meng,

00:42:11.880 --> 00:42:12.880
here's the thing.

00:42:13.510 --> 00:42:15.280
I know we are in a crisis,

00:42:15.590 --> 00:42:16.590
but for you,

00:42:17.030 --> 00:42:19.230
isn't our factory a juicy piece of meat?

00:42:19.880 --> 00:42:22.030
Then tell me, where is the value?

00:42:22.570 --> 00:42:23.820
Then let me tell you,

00:42:25.110 --> 00:42:26.360
we have channels,

00:42:26.360 --> 00:42:28.400
clients, and technical patents.

00:42:28.790 --> 00:42:30.850
Isn't that why you want to acquire us?

00:42:31.510 --> 00:42:32.630
Little girl, if you don't know
how to negotiate,

00:42:32.630 --> 00:42:33.490
let him do this.

00:42:34.250 --> 00:42:36.590
Even though you hold
the most critical assets,

00:42:36.590 --> 00:42:38.230
these assets don't make money;
they only make you lose money.

00:42:38.230 --> 00:42:40.630
Don't you still
have to sell in the end anyway?

00:42:40.630 --> 00:42:41.670
I do want to sell.

00:42:42.550 --> 00:42:44.750
But a sale is a sale, no matter the buyer.

00:42:45.000 --> 00:42:46.400
You happen to want to buy,

00:42:47.150 --> 00:42:48.070
and you're in charge.

00:42:48.070 --> 00:42:50.400
I just want to work with you.
Is that wrong?

00:42:50.830 --> 00:42:53.020
To be honest, you know my background.

00:42:53.510 --> 00:42:55.170
I trust you to get things done.

00:42:56.150 --> 00:42:57.360
You guys talk. I'm stepping out.